Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.52,0:00:04.61,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(290,260)\fad(400,400)}生\N\N日
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.25,0:00:02.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.78,0:00:05.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們為名乃開生日會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.59,0:00:08.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊  什麼時候呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.30,0:00:08.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.95,0:00:09.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本日？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.17,0:00:13.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  那你就得事先告訴我們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.25,0:00:14.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.64,0:00:17.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.18,0:00:19.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什麼準備都沒做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.10,0:00:23.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  今天也不是名乃的生日啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.10,0:00:25.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒問過她嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.30,0:00:26.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.18,0:00:26.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.04,0:00:28.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是驚喜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.31,0:00:29.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.70,0:00:30.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士的…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.57,0:00:34.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士的生日會也一起辦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.98,0:00:38.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊  真是一石二鳥  辦吧辦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.93,0:00:44.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種意外驚喜  不管是策劃的還是接受的都很開心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.04,0:00:50.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  我知道了  那大家就在回家路上去買蛋糕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.83,0:00:53.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  麻衣OK嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.77,0:00:55.01,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}這裡的錢包專指那種金屬卡口蛙口型小錢包。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.77,0:00:55.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我忘帶錢包了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.62,0:00:58.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒…沒辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.76,0:01:00.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼祐子就和我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.61,0:01:02.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也忘記帶錢包了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.36,0:01:05.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美緒  拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.56,0:01:11.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前去遊樂園弄掉的錢還沒還你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.50,0:01:15.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之今天就由我來出吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.54,0:01:19.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我去對名乃說「我們給你辦生日會」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.80,0:01:21.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驚喜到哪裡去了啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.67,0:01:26.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  祐子是笨蛋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.78,0:01:32.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你明明被笹原學長甩掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.62,0:01:35.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我沒有被甩啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.82,0:01:37.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明哭著逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.48,0:01:41.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是…  話說他們只是挽著手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.39,0:01:43.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並不知道他們是否有在交往對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.96,0:01:46.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒有向他本人確認
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.73,0:01:48.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說還沒有完全被甩不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.45,0:01:52.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我還沒有完全放棄啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.48,0:01:54.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是很喜歡他的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.51,0:02:05.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.93,0:02:18.06,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(60,290)\fad(600,600)}日\N常\N之\N110
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.91,0:02:16.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好  沒有忘帶的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.97,0:02:19.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士  那我出門了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.10,0:02:22.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.36,0:02:35.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事  博士
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.50,0:02:38.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才我做了個「小傢伙」  所以取下來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.82,0:02:45.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士  「小傢伙」是指什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.01,0:02:49.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「小傢伙」就是  我看看…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.39,0:02:53.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那東西能讓背上變得光滑嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.19,0:02:55.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.34,0:02:59.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然小  但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.20,0:03:04.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.85,0:03:05.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.45,0:03:06.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.62,0:03:07.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.69,0:03:10.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃  你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.43,0:03:13.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一大早你們就在做什麼啊  吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.05,0:03:19.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鬼  你又造了什麼陷阱啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.66,0:03:22.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阪本把小傢伙弄壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.03,0:03:28.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.45,0:03:31.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…那個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.08,0:03:34.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阪本把名乃弄哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.27,0:03:37.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不不  是把它亂放的你的錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.88,0:03:40.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去學校了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.85,0:03:47.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃  你忘帶東西了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.95,0:03:52.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.36,0:03:56.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還能馬上重做一個的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.05,0:04:00.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來之前能做好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.74,0:04:02.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我現在就去做
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.06,0:04:09.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士  我去學校了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.52,0:04:13.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出發了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.75,0:04:16.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.09,0:04:18.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.20,0:00:00.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.02,0:04:28.25,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(290,335)\fad(500,00)\fs40}校\N長\N與\N教\N導\N主\N任
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.18,0:04:27.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  好奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.84,0:04:29.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教導主任
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.72,0:04:36.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是以前我還在校長的王座上時期的銅像啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.89,0:04:42.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好奇怪啊  這裡應該放著的是東雲校長的才對啊  好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.47,0:04:51.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  最近的年輕人的惡作劇該說是幽默呢還是惡趣味呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.15,0:04:53.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎樣的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.73,0:04:57.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是有支持者的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.55,0:05:03.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主任老師  搬運完畢了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.53,0:05:06.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這座銅像這樣放就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.06,0:05:10.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什麼都沒…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.12,0:05:17.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教導主任  這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.92,0:05:25.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真…真是的  最近年輕人的惡作劇讓人怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.58,0:05:27.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是花心思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.08,0:05:32.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱…抱歉  這座銅像也運走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.72,0:05:35.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒  要把這便宜貨收拾掉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.99,0:05:36.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便宜貨…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.90,0:05:40.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了  那我就把這土裡土氣的東西搬走了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.67,0:05:41.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土裡土氣…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.65,0:05:44.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  把這礙事的東西搬走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.09,0:05:51.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  教導主任  不要介意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.17,0:05:54.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼把剛才那座愚蠢的銅像也搬走哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.26,0:05:55.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.02,0:05:58.68,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(290,340)\fad(500,00)}圍\N棋\N足\N球\N部\N8
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.20,0:06:08.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？  門沒鎖
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.03,0:06:16.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊  關口你在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.71,0:06:18.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還以為我是第一個到的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.59,0:06:20.37,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}也就是SR-71高空戰略偵察機，愛稱黑鳥。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.59,0:06:20.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還特地乘了黑鳥來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.21,0:06:23.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼  關口要來早練嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.89,0:06:28.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…  那個…  那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.42,0:06:32.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.40,0:06:34.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.33,0:06:57.45,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(50,290)\fad(600,00)}日\N常\N之\N111
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.75,0:06:56.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們的午飯居然都要我出錢…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.01,0:06:57.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.19,0:07:01.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  沒帶錢包也是沒辦法的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.04,0:07:04.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是美緒  給你一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.37,0:07:08.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒…沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.28,0:07:11.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  祐子你打太重了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.88,0:07:13.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.67,0:07:17.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.68,0:07:19.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.20,0:07:25.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說來  祐子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.73,0:07:28.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有問過名乃今天有空嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.34,0:07:30.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  完全忘記了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.22,0:07:34.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  那我就去和她說辦生日會的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.31,0:07:36.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.88,0:07:38.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就問下今天有沒有空就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.00,0:07:40.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.54,0:07:41.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.18,0:07:43.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  我去好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.92,0:07:45.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說了我去嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.97,0:07:47.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.45,0:07:48.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去就行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.59,0:07:49.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.17,0:07:51.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.46,0:07:55.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…  麻衣麻衣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.37,0:07:56.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Moment please
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.50,0:07:57.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just moment please
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.70,0:08:04.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我稍微去名乃那兒一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.53,0:08:05.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全速前進
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.61,0:08:14.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對…對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.86,0:08:18.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要在意  去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.93,0:08:22.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是對不起  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.86,0:08:24.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.99,0:08:34.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  要成純咖啡了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.80,0:08:35.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.10,0:08:37.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.15,0:08:39.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才要說對不起的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.84,0:08:41.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.87,0:08:47.52,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}中獎了  如果中獎可以再來一瓶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.55,0:09:05.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相…相生同學  在走廊上要安靜…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.24,0:09:16.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彩虹
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.31,0:09:29.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.61,0:09:48.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛痛痛痛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.65,0:09:49.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相生同學
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.10,0:09:51.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.00,0:09:53.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃  我正在找你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.63,0:09:55.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.88,0:09:57.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  實際上…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.71,0:10:01.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…這個是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.58,0:10:04.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事嗎  不痛吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.54,0:10:07.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.05,0:10:09.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.12,0:10:14.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  這不是你想的那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.73,0:10:16.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.16,0:10:19.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐呐  比起這個  今天可以去名乃家嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.20,0:10:23.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  對了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.12,0:10:27.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這是驚喜  我不會說的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.97,0:10:28.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.83,0:10:30.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就回見啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.20,0:10:32.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.96,0:10:41.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼也去買相生同學他們的份吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.25,0:10:50.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先出石頭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.92,0:10:52.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後出布
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.64,0:10:54.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要亂出喲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.45,0:10:55.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石頭剪刀布！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.13,0:10:58.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.87,0:11:11.38,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(60,290)\fad(600,00)}日\N常\N之\N112
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.32,0:12:41.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個南瓜…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.86,0:12:42.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好硬！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.94,0:12:49.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  那小鬼為什麼要一次又一次
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.01,0:12:50.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大將
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.03,0:12:51.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是大將嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.44,0:12:54.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大將
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.30,0:12:55.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中…中村
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.25,0:12:58.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正在找你  大將  沒事太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.68,0:13:02.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要逃走啊  忘記我了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.62,0:13:04.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為沒有忘記才要逃走的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.18,0:13:07.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大將吃飯了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.62,0:13:09.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.97,0:13:16.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了大將  不吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.70,0:13:23.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了大將
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.46,0:13:25.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洗白白了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.11,0:13:28.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.79,0:13:31.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大將
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.66,0:13:34.54,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}機器人研究  和貓生活
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.24,0:13:34.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了  不快點出門會遲到的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.73,0:13:37.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大將  那麼我就出門了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.18,0:13:41.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.04,0:13:50.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大將  快出來啊  大將
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.39,0:13:52.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大將～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.51,0:13:55.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕快走啊你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.41,0:13:57.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？  中村老師
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.82,0:13:58.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,午安
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.14,0:13:59.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,東雲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.42,0:14:01.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姑娘  快做點什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.26,0:14:06.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您在幹什麼  是在找什麼東西嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.80,0:14:07.75,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}注：撲火的是夏天的蛾子。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.80,0:14:07.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就叫撲火的夏天機器人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.51,0:14:11.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是東雲在學校什麼時候都能見到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.61,0:14:15.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在要優先找大將
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.67,0:14:18.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  東雲  你有看到一隻黑貓嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.51,0:14:22.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中村老師家有黑貓嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.38,0:14:25.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢  但是不見了的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.32,0:14:28.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家也有一隻黑貓哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.16,0:14:29.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.53,0:14:32.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我幫您一起找可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.04,0:14:35.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思啊  東雲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.28,0:14:35.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.68,0:14:38.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是白癡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.81,0:14:40.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了中村老師
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.52,0:14:43.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師的貓的名字叫做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.06,0:14:44.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大將
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.69,0:14:48.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是有意思的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.69,0:14:53.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家黑貓的名字叫做阪本先生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.87,0:14:55.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好奇怪的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.15,0:14:58.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是奇怪的名字呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.55,0:15:03.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它可愛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.58,0:15:06.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大將  可愛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.16,0:15:11.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你在說什麼啊你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.85,0:15:16.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  中村也沒有什麼惡意
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.72,0:15:23.63,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}關於笨手笨腳的中村的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.28,0:15:21.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  老這麼出岔子我可受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.03,0:15:25.61,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}關於惡作劇小鬼的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.18,0:15:26.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  等等  現在不也沒有改變嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.37,0:15:30.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天平不會移動
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.58,0:15:33.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…已經這個時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.80,0:15:35.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  中村老師
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.78,0:15:38.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我差不多該回去了  食物的新鮮度…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.59,0:15:41.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.63,0:15:45.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是找到了  我能去看大將嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.34,0:15:48.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧  什麼時候都行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.16,0:15:49.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天就來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.55,0:15:53.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我先告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.92,0:16:04.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可…可惡  無論去哪邊都糟透了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.44,0:16:08.55,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(270,290)\fad(600,600)}日\N常\N之\N113
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.08,0:16:10.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士  阪本先生  我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.21,0:16:12.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.62,0:16:14.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.39,0:16:18.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成了嗎  博士
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.45,0:16:20.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又被阪本踩壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.68,0:16:23.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阪本先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.90,0:16:31.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？  取下來可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.46,0:16:33.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上就做一個
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.17,0:16:37.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.13,0:16:43.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  如此簡單就能取下來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.40,0:16:47.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自己想取下來卻完全沒辦法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.46,0:16:52.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為名乃自己取不了  要別人取才行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.60,0:16:53.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.75,0:16:57.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是如果是名乃自己就能裝上去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.27,0:16:58.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這算什麼機能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.16,0:17:04.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說博士  那個小傢伙有什麼機能呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.82,0:17:09.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是取下來的話  大拇趾就飛不出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.35,0:17:11.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有那個機能…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.11,0:17:14.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是相生同學他們呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.46,0:17:17.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.60,0:17:20.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐子來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.44,0:17:26.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  對了  得把發條收起來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.02,0:17:31.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣我就能看上去像個普通人了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.56,0:17:35.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能比現在更融入大家了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.63,0:17:40.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和大家出去玩的時候  都能更普通地享受了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.79,0:17:42.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日常生活在等著我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.07,0:17:47.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶吶  比起這個  今天可以去名乃家嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.02,0:17:52.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為很可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.11,0:17:57.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃就是名乃  這樣就好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.71,0:18:00.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我是為了說這句話而來的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.35,0:18:02.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都忘記了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.28,0:18:17.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.86,0:18:19.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.40,0:18:20.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.50,0:18:34.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安靜點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.93,0:18:36.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是重要的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.55,0:18:37.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.21,0:18:40.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一…二
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.90,0:18:42.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.92,0:18:47.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生日快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.93,0:18:49.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們買蛋糕來了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.57,0:18:50.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相生同學
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.07,0:18:53.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生日…  為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.16,0:18:58.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是驚喜哦  驚喜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.44,0:19:00.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛋糕  我要吃蛋糕  蛋糕…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.75,0:19:03.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  博士  別著急嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.52,0:19:05.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  博士
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.19,0:19:06.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別急  博士
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.72,0:19:10.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.75,0:19:11.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛋糕…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.85,0:19:13.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎怎怎怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.40,0:19:14.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.83,0:19:15.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡還有一個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.15,0:19:17.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.01,0:19:18.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.01,0:19:19.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.92,0:19:34.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是大家為什麼會知道啊  我的生日
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.87,0:19:42.14,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}名乃的生日
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.47,0:19:51.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.38,0:19:54.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小傢伙做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.18,0:19:55.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.11,0:20:01.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然確實這個發條帶來了很多不便
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.14,0:20:04.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我超級想要取下來的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.16,0:20:13.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我保持這個樣子就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.24,0:20:20.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個小傢伙其實是個名乃高興的時候發條會轉起來的裝置
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.82,0:20:22.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這算什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.44,0:20:27.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…對了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.30,0:20:31.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士  你能把這個蛋糕端出去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.44,0:20:33.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又一個蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.90,0:20:35.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把茶端過去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.96,0:20:36.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.76,0:20:40.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛋糕  蛋糕…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.69,0:20:42.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.99,0:20:45.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛋糕…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.78,0:20:47.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  你們倆在做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.92,0:20:50.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相生同學  你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.12,0:20:53.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃  快找個東西擦一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.53,0:20:54.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.37,0:20:55.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡插上蠟燭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.40,0:20:57.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好狡猾  博士我也要插
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.91,0:21:00.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣  在這之前先要做好準備啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.77,0:21:02.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擦的東西  擦的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.73,0:21:08.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.22,0:21:11.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  那個那個
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.66,0:21:14.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再插一根
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.45,0:21:16.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦  先要準備好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.26,0:21:19.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣  快停下  快停下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
